***************
*** 315,318 ****
--- 315,319 ----

$CN = $args{name} . &#34; $num&#34;;
+     print &#34;$CN&#92;n&#34;;
# setup config file for the openssl stuff
umask 0x600;</pre></div><div class='update_description'><i onclick="document.location='10943#1315936787'; reset_anchor();" class="pull-right icon icon-share"></i><div class="header"><time datetime="2011-09-13T17:59:47+00:00">Sep 13, 2011 05:59 PM UTC</time> by <b>Ian Stokes-Rees</b><a class="anchor" name="1315936787">&nbsp;</a></div><pre>To the best of my knowledge the software hasn&#39;t been updated in the past 2 weeks, so I assume the same problem remains.  I submitted this as a comment to the cert-renew software devlopers.  GOC probably isn&#39;t the best place to track software bugs, feature requests, and suggestions for improvements.

